{"MOXA":[{"def":"A soft woolly mass prepared from the young leaves of Artemisia Chinensis, and used as a cautery by burning it on the skin; hence, any substance used in a like manner, as cotton impregnated with niter, amadou.","pos":""},{"def":"A plant from which this substance is obtained, esp.","pos":""}],"MOXIE":[{"def":"Know-how, expertise.","pos":""}]}